WEBVTT

00:01:19.039 --> 00:01:19.640
Old Yan.

00:01:19.840 --> 00:01:21.170
I found something here.

00:01:36.039 --> 00:01:36.560
This...

00:01:37.440 --> 00:01:38.600
He's been moved.

00:01:39.680 --> 00:01:40.640
In such a short time,

00:01:40.640 --> 00:01:42.640
he couldn't have disguised himself

00:01:42.759 --> 00:01:43.960
and completed the transfer.

00:01:43.960 --> 00:01:45.120
Maybe Zhang Wendong

00:01:45.479 --> 00:01:47.440
never came to this event site.

00:01:48.520 --> 00:01:49.450
This bloodstain

00:01:50.039 --> 00:01:51.160
must have seeped from

00:01:51.160 --> 00:01:52.560
the prop box above

00:01:52.680 --> 00:01:54.210
or scraped onto it earlier.

00:01:54.320 --> 00:01:55.039
That means

00:01:55.039 --> 00:01:58.320
he had already been moved when he reached the village entrance.

00:01:58.320 --> 00:01:59.450
Find their manager.

00:01:59.600 --> 00:01:59.960
Yes.

00:02:01.040 --> 00:02:01.400
Right.

00:02:01.400 --> 00:02:01.930
Exactly.

00:02:02.280 --> 00:02:03.720
There was a box like that.

00:02:03.960 --> 00:02:04.620
Where is it?

00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:07.320
It was shipped out long ago.

00:02:07.320 --> 00:02:07.960
They said before

00:02:07.960 --> 00:02:09.039
it would just be one trip.

00:02:09.039 --> 00:02:10.440
Someone would pick up the goods,

00:02:10.440 --> 00:02:11.760
and they'd be back soon.

00:02:11.760 --> 00:02:12.280
But now...

00:02:12.280 --> 00:02:13.680
The event is almost over.

00:02:14.280 --> 00:02:14.800
If I had known,

00:02:14.800 --> 00:02:16.480
I wouldn't have taken this lousy job from him.

00:02:16.480 --> 00:02:17.880
What did that person look like?

00:02:17.880 --> 00:02:18.810
I don't know him.

00:02:18.880 --> 00:02:20.000
He was wearing a big mask.

00:02:20.000 --> 00:02:20.880
I saw his price

00:02:20.880 --> 00:02:21.810
was high enough,

00:02:22.120 --> 00:02:23.040
so I agreed.

00:02:23.120 --> 00:02:24.980
Where did he ask you to deliver it?

00:02:25.920 --> 00:02:26.880
The intersection of Maoyi Street

00:02:26.880 --> 00:02:28.440
and Renhe Road.

00:02:28.960 --> 00:02:31.160
He said someone would come to pick it up.

00:02:31.280 --> 00:02:32.040
That area

00:02:32.440 --> 00:02:33.880
is the former site of Huguang.

00:02:33.880 --> 00:02:35.760
It's the starting point of his murder plan.

00:02:35.760 --> 00:02:37.280
He probably also wants to make it

00:02:37.280 --> 00:02:39.079
the final act of his murder plan.

00:02:40.280 --> 00:02:41.810
We have to hurry over there.

00:04:07.840 --> 00:04:08.520
Split up.

00:05:06.400 --> 00:05:07.400
Save the victims.

00:05:07.480 --> 00:05:08.200
Call an ambulance.

00:05:08.200 --> 00:05:08.730
Yes, sir.

00:05:12.200 --> 00:05:13.640
That man was wearing a hat.

00:05:13.640 --> 00:05:14.200
It was too dark.

00:05:14.200 --> 00:05:15.480
I didn't see his face clearly.

00:05:15.480 --> 00:05:16.960
When the killer was cutting,

00:05:16.960 --> 00:05:17.840
she was still alive.

00:05:17.840 --> 00:05:19.120
This is completely insane.

00:05:19.120 --> 00:05:21.200
This is a very rare cause of death.

00:05:21.280 --> 00:05:22.680
Carotid sinus reflex death.

00:05:22.680 --> 00:05:24.280
He doesn't treat murder as a game.

00:05:24.280 --> 00:05:25.640
He treats it as a career.

00:05:25.880 --> 00:05:27.720
He threatens me with my daughter every day.

00:05:27.720 --> 00:05:29.450
I don't know who threw the bomb.

00:05:29.560 --> 00:05:31.720
The greatest thing about a magician is

00:05:31.800 --> 00:05:35.440
perfectly hiding what truly exists.

00:05:59.240 --> 00:06:01.080
This trick of hiding in plain sight

00:06:01.080 --> 00:06:02.280
should come to an end.

00:06:06.240 --> 00:06:07.440
There's no show here.

00:06:07.960 --> 00:06:09.320
You came to the wrong place.

00:06:09.320 --> 00:06:10.720
Your little game is up.

00:06:11.400 --> 00:06:12.240
Come with me.

00:06:13.160 --> 00:06:14.490
You still have a chance.

00:06:16.520 --> 00:06:17.360
What chance do I need?

00:06:17.360 --> 00:06:18.280
A chance to turn yourself in.

00:06:18.280 --> 00:06:19.240
I don't need it.

00:06:19.600 --> 00:06:20.400
Zhou Guannan.

00:06:20.920 --> 00:06:21.520
You are now

00:06:21.520 --> 00:06:23.080
a suspect in a major criminal case.

00:06:23.080 --> 00:06:25.210
Are you going to keep making mistakes?

00:06:29.320 --> 00:06:31.160
If you can prove I'm guilty,

00:06:32.640 --> 00:06:33.760
I'll go with you.

00:06:37.159 --> 00:06:38.290
I never believed it.

00:06:40.200 --> 00:06:41.320
Even when all the evidence

00:06:41.320 --> 00:06:42.280
pointed to you,

00:06:43.320 --> 00:06:44.840
I kept deceiving myself.

00:06:48.240 --> 00:06:49.280
Until today,

00:06:50.560 --> 00:06:52.640
when I saw your profile in the video,

00:06:54.280 --> 00:06:55.540
I finally understood.

00:07:11.360 --> 00:07:12.520
What do you know?

00:07:15.720 --> 00:07:16.760
During college,

00:07:17.120 --> 00:07:19.980
you secretly studied at Richudongfang Art School.

00:07:20.520 --> 00:07:21.650
You studied acting.

00:07:22.120 --> 00:07:23.360
Li Ting and Guan Jing

00:07:23.400 --> 00:07:24.800
were both your schoolmates.

00:07:24.800 --> 00:07:26.280
Your motive was revenge.

00:07:26.440 --> 00:07:27.720
You were getting revenge for Guan Jing,

00:07:27.720 --> 00:07:30.000
who was tortured to death by Zhang Wendong and the others.

00:07:30.000 --> 00:07:31.360
For every person you killed,

00:07:31.360 --> 00:07:32.880
you would visit her grave

00:07:33.320 --> 00:07:34.780
and leave a pot of flowers.

00:07:34.960 --> 00:07:38.280
You think you're carrying out justice for heaven, don't you?

00:07:38.280 --> 00:07:39.440
In Qiao Sisi's case,

00:07:40.040 --> 00:07:42.970
the cripple smoking foreign cigarettes in the taxi,

00:07:44.240 --> 00:07:45.760
the person who kept playing Ma Jinguang

00:07:45.760 --> 00:07:47.560
to distract our investigation,

00:07:48.120 --> 00:07:49.840
the one who detonated the mine,

00:07:49.840 --> 00:07:52.640
the one who pretended to be lame and killed Hao Weiguo,

00:07:52.640 --> 00:07:53.960
the person who instigated Wang Guifang

00:07:53.960 --> 00:07:55.040
to stalk Liu Jiang,

00:07:55.040 --> 00:07:57.120
the one who bombed Jia Peng to death in Lianshui,

00:07:57.120 --> 00:07:58.520
and the one who kidnapped Zhang Wendong.

00:07:58.520 --> 00:07:58.960
They

00:07:58.960 --> 00:08:01.490
are all characters you created, aren't they?

00:08:06.560 --> 00:08:07.200
What else?

00:08:07.640 --> 00:08:08.440
Zhou Guannan,

00:08:08.840 --> 00:08:10.000
it's not too late to turn yourself in.

00:08:10.000 --> 00:08:11.530
Don't be stubborn anymore.

00:08:12.920 --> 00:08:14.780
I don't want to arrest you myself.

00:08:17.080 --> 00:08:17.720
Yan Mi.

00:08:19.920 --> 00:08:22.720
What makes you think you can catch me?

00:08:28.880 --> 00:08:30.740
When you attacked Zhang Wendong,

00:08:30.800 --> 00:08:32.059
you were holding a gun.

00:08:33.000 --> 00:08:34.200
Where did you hide it?

00:08:35.320 --> 00:08:37.039
The last time I came to your house,

00:08:37.039 --> 00:08:39.280
I asked property management for the floor plan of this apartment.

00:08:39.280 --> 00:08:40.210
Compared to now,

00:08:40.240 --> 00:08:42.480
there's a discrepancy of nearly ten square meters.

00:08:42.480 --> 00:08:44.540
You hid all your secrets and evidence

00:08:46.720 --> 00:08:48.560
in those ten square meters.

00:09:37.960 --> 00:09:38.620
Don't move.

00:09:39.040 --> 00:09:40.040
Put your hands up.

00:09:47.680 --> 00:09:49.000
That gun was fake,

00:09:49.080 --> 00:09:50.680
but this is real.

00:09:51.800 --> 00:09:53.480
There are no cops outside.

00:09:54.040 --> 00:09:55.570
You came alone, didn't you?

00:09:55.600 --> 00:09:56.400
Zhou Guannan,

00:09:57.000 --> 00:09:58.000
you can't escape.

00:09:58.160 --> 00:09:59.960
If you shoot, I'll detonate it.

00:10:00.520 --> 00:10:02.580
I have a lot of neighbors around here.

00:10:04.040 --> 00:10:06.170
You wouldn't want your impulsiveness

00:10:06.240 --> 00:10:08.320
to make them die in vain, would you?

00:10:15.440 --> 00:10:16.560
Put the gun down.

00:11:05.560 --> 00:11:06.200
Why?

00:11:10.760 --> 00:11:13.000
There's never a why.

00:11:13.880 --> 00:11:15.240
You always try

00:11:15.240 --> 00:11:17.520
to find a pretty excuse for evil.

00:11:17.640 --> 00:11:19.440
That's why you keep failing.

00:11:20.560 --> 00:11:23.020
You already crawled your way back from hell.

00:11:23.400 --> 00:11:24.480
I watched you

00:11:25.880 --> 00:11:27.610
suffer through agonizing pain

00:11:27.960 --> 00:11:29.400
to crawl your way back.

00:11:30.080 --> 00:11:31.040
But why must you

00:11:31.400 --> 00:11:33.600
turn your life into a living hell again?

00:11:34.040 --> 00:11:35.440
How does acting like this

00:11:36.320 --> 00:11:38.040
honor your late parents?

00:11:44.520 --> 00:11:46.400
Why should I feel sorry for them?

00:11:47.440 --> 00:11:49.480
Aren't you the one who let them down?

00:11:49.720 --> 00:11:52.080
And those animals, the Ma father and son?

00:11:53.000 --> 00:11:54.800
Yan Mi, I am really curious.

00:11:56.320 --> 00:11:58.560
You have a bomb strapped to you right now.

00:11:58.560 --> 00:12:00.080
Why are you still so calm?

00:12:00.640 --> 00:12:02.400
I have killed so many people.

00:12:03.680 --> 00:12:05.000
Don't you hate me?

00:12:06.040 --> 00:12:09.240
I don't see a hint of disgust in your eyes.

00:12:09.360 --> 00:12:10.880
Only pity.

00:12:12.520 --> 00:12:14.720
I don't need your pity.

00:12:16.000 --> 00:12:16.640
Yan Mi.

00:12:17.760 --> 00:12:19.440
You only know that I hate you,

00:12:19.920 --> 00:12:21.320
but you never understand

00:12:21.400 --> 00:12:24.120
why I hate you to the bone.

00:12:25.720 --> 00:12:28.920
I've been a stray dog thrown by the stinking ditch since I was a child.

00:12:28.920 --> 00:12:31.240
No one has ever looked me in the eye.

00:12:31.240 --> 00:12:33.170
Nor has anyone cared about my life.

00:12:33.840 --> 00:12:34.800
It was Zhou Gang.

00:12:35.240 --> 00:12:37.240
He picked me up when I was freezing

00:12:37.240 --> 00:12:38.840
and warmed me in his arms.

00:12:39.560 --> 00:12:41.480
It was my mom, with tears in her eyes,

00:12:41.480 --> 00:12:45.480
who fed hot soup and rice into my starving stomach bite by bite.

00:12:46.520 --> 00:12:47.720
What they gave me

00:12:47.920 --> 00:12:49.000
was not a home.

00:12:49.880 --> 00:12:52.120
They pulled me out of the mud,

00:12:52.120 --> 00:12:54.600
washed me clean, warmed me up, and then told me.

00:12:54.600 --> 00:12:56.680
I can also be someone's light.

00:12:57.120 --> 00:12:58.680
They gave me all

00:12:58.720 --> 00:13:00.720
their love and respect.

00:13:01.200 --> 00:13:01.960
Hurry up.

00:13:02.040 --> 00:13:04.440
Even though I went against his greatest expectations

00:13:04.440 --> 00:13:06.520
and willfully studied acting.

00:13:06.880 --> 00:13:09.410
You still have a chance to be a police officer.

00:13:09.640 --> 00:13:11.570
I don't want to be a police officer.

00:13:12.440 --> 00:13:13.840
I just want to focus on art

00:13:13.880 --> 00:13:14.880
and become an actor in the future.

00:13:14.880 --> 00:13:15.640
Guannan.

00:13:24.320 --> 00:13:25.450
Thought it through?

00:13:25.760 --> 00:13:26.760
Made up your mind?

00:13:36.280 --> 00:13:37.410
You're an adult now.

00:13:38.040 --> 00:13:40.500
You have the right to choose your own future.

00:13:40.640 --> 00:13:42.520
No matter what choice you make,

00:13:44.560 --> 00:13:46.220
your mother and I support you.

00:13:51.600 --> 00:13:52.330
Thanks, Dad.

00:13:52.840 --> 00:13:53.570
Thanks, Mom.

00:13:55.040 --> 00:13:56.080
But this light,

00:13:56.720 --> 00:13:57.920
this human life.

00:13:58.320 --> 00:14:01.400
This is the life I begged for on my knees.

00:14:01.960 --> 00:14:03.000
And it was blown away

00:14:03.000 --> 00:14:05.160
by a set of car keys you casually lent out,

00:14:05.160 --> 00:14:06.490
completely destroyed.

00:14:07.440 --> 00:14:09.360
Blown away clean,

00:14:09.800 --> 00:14:12.320
along with this face they hoped would make it to the big screen.

00:14:12.320 --> 00:14:14.200
All blown to pieces.

00:14:15.200 --> 00:14:16.400
Yan Mi, tell me.

00:14:16.560 --> 00:14:17.400
Besides hatred

00:14:17.400 --> 00:14:20.240
and dragging this awful world into the fire,

00:14:20.280 --> 00:14:22.480
what else can I hold on to?

00:14:25.840 --> 00:14:27.240
If back then,

00:14:28.200 --> 00:14:30.240
you hadn't lent the car to my dad,

00:14:33.000 --> 00:14:35.880
would everything be different now?

00:14:38.040 --> 00:14:40.400
Everything would be different, right?

00:14:43.320 --> 00:14:45.180
Of course, it would be different.

00:14:46.320 --> 00:14:48.440
You would be standing in the spotlight.

00:14:48.440 --> 00:14:51.200
Your parents would clap until their hands were red,

00:14:51.200 --> 00:14:52.600
with tears in their eyes,

00:14:52.720 --> 00:14:53.960
and pride on their faces.

00:14:53.960 --> 00:14:55.520
But with everything you are doing now,

00:14:55.520 --> 00:14:56.320
Zhou Guannan,

00:14:56.800 --> 00:14:57.840
you are personally

00:14:57.840 --> 00:14:59.360
stomping the popularity your parents built for you

00:14:59.360 --> 00:15:01.760
into mud dirtier than a gutter.

00:15:06.080 --> 00:15:07.800
You shouldn't have taken this path.

00:15:07.800 --> 00:15:08.520
Why?

00:15:09.360 --> 00:15:10.120
Just because

00:15:10.560 --> 00:15:12.440
the one who adopted me was a cop.

00:15:13.720 --> 00:15:16.400
But what good are you cops anyway?

00:15:17.240 --> 00:15:19.080
Good people are blown to pieces,

00:15:19.720 --> 00:15:21.960
and you can't do anything about it.

00:15:23.120 --> 00:15:25.760
How could I possibly count on you again?

00:15:26.440 --> 00:15:27.280
Stop.

00:15:28.240 --> 00:15:29.320
Let it all end.

00:15:29.360 --> 00:15:30.690
It ended a long time ago.

00:15:32.800 --> 00:15:35.000
It ended a long time ago.

00:15:35.520 --> 00:15:37.040
I, Zhou Guannan,

00:15:37.920 --> 00:15:40.920
already died on the last day of being nineteen.

00:15:42.520 --> 00:15:44.440
Before getting in the car that day,

00:15:44.440 --> 00:15:45.320
my mom said

00:15:45.600 --> 00:15:47.000
I'd be an adult tomorrow,

00:15:47.280 --> 00:15:49.740
and she wanted to cook me longevity noodles.

00:15:49.880 --> 00:15:51.000
But the next day,

00:15:51.600 --> 00:15:53.360
the sun never rose again.

00:15:53.960 --> 00:15:55.200
All that survived

00:15:55.520 --> 00:15:56.880
was this pile of rotting flesh

00:15:56.880 --> 00:15:58.400
and hatred for this world.

00:15:59.920 --> 00:16:01.040
I am now

00:16:01.720 --> 00:16:03.400
a wandering ghost.

00:16:06.080 --> 00:16:08.280
But even as a ghost,

00:16:09.960 --> 00:16:11.600
I am free.

00:16:13.160 --> 00:16:15.160
I will never fall into your hands.

00:16:17.960 --> 00:16:19.640
It's time to say goodbye.

00:16:30.960 --> 00:16:31.760
Zhou Guannan.

00:16:32.440 --> 00:16:33.720
If you walk out this door,

00:16:33.720 --> 00:16:35.120
there is no turning back.